      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-dem-min-000      thru vis-dem-min-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Prompt data emissione massima da ricercare      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dem-max-000      thru pmt-dem-max-999        .
